---
title: Sticky Spanish Chicken with Parsley Rice and Peas
description: Chicken thighs are the most succulent part of the chicken and are delicious in this dish. We’ve jazzed up the rice with some onion, garlic, coriander and peas which is the perfect accompaniment to this spicy sticky chicken. It’s so quick and easy you will be amazed at the taste sensation you can produce in such a short period of time!
